                    <i class="fas fa-code" style="font-size: 2rem; color: #1995AD;"></i>
                </div>
                <h5 class="card-title">Projects</h5>
                <p class="card-text">Explore my latest projects and see how I bring ideas to life through clean code and thoughtful design.</p>
