        </div>
    </div>
    <div class="col-md-4">
        <div class="card h-100">
            <div class="card-body text-center">
                <div class="mb-3">
                    <i class="fas fa-laptop-code" style="font-size: 2rem; color: #1995AD;"></i>
                </div>
                <h5 class="card-title">Skills</h5>
                <p class="card-text">From front-end finesse to back-end brilliance, discover my technical expertise and professional journey.</p>
                <a href="/skills" class="btn btn-primary">Learn More</a>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
    <div class="col-md-4">
        <div class="card h-100">
            <div class="card-body text-center">
                <div class="mb-3">
                    <i class="fas fa-envelope" style="font-size: 2rem; color: #1995AD;"></i>
                </div>
                <h5 class="card-title">Let's Connect</h5>
                <p class="card-text">Have a project in mind? I'd love to hear about it. Let's create something amazing together.</p>
                <a href="/contact" class="btn btn-primary">Contact Me</a>
