                    <i class="fas fa-lightbulb mb-3" style="font-size: 2rem; color: #A1D6E2;"></i>
                    <h5>Creative Solutions</h5>
                    <p class="text-muted">Innovative approaches to solve complex problems</p>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="col-md-6 col-lg-3">
                <div class="p-4 rounded" style="background-color: #fff;">
                    <i class="fas fa-mobile-alt mb-3" style="font-size: 2rem; color: #A1D6E2;"></i>
